official_title: Self-Collection of the Pap Smear as Agency: A Novel Way to Improve Refractory Low Cervical Cancer Screening Rates in Rural Alabama
inclusion_criteria:
* Female of at least 21 years of age and not over 65 presenting who need routine cervical cancer screening per national guidelines.
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 21 Years
Must have maximum age of 65 Years
exclusion_criteria: * prior history of cervical cancer or a positive Pap smear, have had a total hysterectomy (removal of uterus and cervix), or currently enrolled in any other cancer prevention study.
